channel.description:
[img]http://img33.imageshack.us/img33/8614/uhmwierd.jpg[/img]
Why is there dwarf remains there?
Wasn't like this yesterday.. I never even TOUCHED anything in the dueling area, and now its like this? :s
help
EDIT - Just tested out something. the account (mrfuzzy) my friend account created yesterday, doesn't show the dwarf remains, but when I create an account or use an account created earlier on today, it shows dwarf remains.
I honestly forget what I did today or coded, so.. I dont think it's client side anymore. COULD BE but I doubt it, considering we both have the same client, cache and files.
